text: The 1991–92 Algerian Championnat National was the 30th season of the Algerian Championnat National since its establishment in 1962. A total of 16 teams contested the league, with MO Constantine as the defending champions, The Championnat started on October 24, 1991. and ended on October 12, 1992. ==Team summaries== === Promotion and relegation === Teams promoted from Algerian Division 2 1991-1992 * US Chaouia * WA Mostaganem * USM Blida Teams relegated to Algerian Division 2 1992-1993 * ES Guelma * USM Bel-Abbès * JSM Tiaret ==League table== ==References== ==External links== *1991–92 Algerian Championnat National Algerian Championnat National Championnat National Category:Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1 seasons
